{"pageid":2120,"pagename":"The Restless Ghost","title":"The Restless Ghost","displaytitle":"The Restless Ghost","revid":14265909,"properties":[{"name":"smw-semanticdata-status","value":""},{"name":"kartographer_frames","value":1},{"name":"page_image_free","value":"The_Restless_Ghost.png"},{"name":"description","value":"A ghost is haunting Lumbridge graveyard. The priest of the Lumbridge church of Saradomin wants you to find out how to get rid of it."}],"content":"<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"noexcerpt noprint nomobile rs-external-header-links\" style=\"display:none\"><span class=\"rs-header-icon rs-header-icon-rs\" data-text=\"RuneScape\" data-title=\"The RuneScape Wiki also has an article on The Restless Ghost.\" data-site=\"rs\">The RuneScape Wiki also has an article on: <a href=\"https://runescape.wiki/w/The_Restless_Ghost\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"rsw:The Restless Ghost\">rsw:The Restless Ghost</a></span><span class=\"rs-header-icon rs-header-icon-rsc\" data-text=\"CS\" data-title=\"The RuneScape Classic Wiki also has an article on The Restless Ghost.\" data-site=\"rsc\">The RuneScape Classic Wiki also has an article on: <a href=\"https://classic.runescape.wiki/w/The_Restless_Ghost\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"classicrsw:The Restless Ghost\">classicrsw:The Restless Ghost</a></span></div>\n<div class=\"hatnote\">\"The Restless Ghost\" redirects here. For the non-player character featured in the quest, see <a href=\"/w/Restless_ghost\" title=\"Restless ghost\">Restless ghost</a>.</div>\n<table class=\"messagebox\" style=\"\">\n<tbody><tr><td style=\"width: 50px;\"><div class=\"center\"><div class=\"floatnone\"><img alt=\"Instruction manual.png\" src=\"/images/Instruction_manual.png?13f14\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"28\" height=\"27\" data-file-width=\"28\" data-file-height=\"27\" /></div></div></td>\n<td><b>This quest has a <a href=\"/w/The_Restless_Ghost/Quick_guide\" title=\"The Restless Ghost/Quick guide\">quick guide found here</a>.</b><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><div style=\"font-size:0.85em; line-height:1.4em;\">It briefly summarises the steps needed to complete the quest.\n</div></td>\n</tr></tbody></table>\n<table class=\"infobox no-parenthesis-style infobox-quest\">\n\n<tbody><tr>\n<th class=\"infobox-header\" colspan=\"5\"><b>The Restless Ghost</b> <span style=\"font-size: 80%;\">(#3)</span>\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"infobox-image infobox-full-width-content\" colspan=\"5\"><a href=\"/w/File:The_Restless_Ghost.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"The Restless Ghost.png\" src=\"/images/thumb/The_Restless_Ghost.png/300px-The_Restless_Ghost.png?a05f9\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"300\" height=\"261\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/The_Restless_Ghost.png/450px-The_Restless_Ghost.png?a05f9 1.5x, /images/thumb/The_Restless_Ghost.png/600px-The_Restless_Ghost.png?a05f9 2x\" data-file-width=\"924\" data-file-height=\"804\" /></a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"infobox-padding\" colspan=\"5\">\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\">Released\n</th>\n<td colspan=\"3\"><a href=\"/w/4_January\" title=\"4 January\">4 January</a> <a href=\"/w/2001\" title=\"2001\">2001</a> (<a href=\"/w/Update:Runescape_beta_is_now_online!\" title=\"Update:Runescape beta is now online!\">Update</a>)\n</td></tr>\n\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/w/Members\" title=\"Members\">Members</a>\n</th>\n<td colspan=\"3\">No\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/w/Quest_series\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Quest series\">Quest series</a>\n</th>\n<td colspan=\"3\">None\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/w/Quest_Difficulties\" title=\"Quest Difficulties\">Official difficulty</a>\n</th>\n<td colspan=\"3\"><a href=\"/w/Quests/Novice\" title=\"Quests/Novice\">Novice</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\">Lead developer(s)\n</th>\n<td colspan=\"3\"><a href=\"https://runescape.wiki/w/Paul_Gower\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"rsw:Paul Gower\">Paul Gower</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"infobox-padding\" colspan=\"5\">\n</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<p>A ghost is haunting <a href=\"/w/Lumbridge\" title=\"Lumbridge\">Lumbridge</a> graveyard. The priest of the Lumbridge church of <a href=\"/w/Saradomin\" title=\"Saradomin\">Saradomin</a> wants you to find out how to get rid of it.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\" role=\"navigation\" aria-labelledby=\"mw-toc-heading\"><input type=\"checkbox\" role=\"button\" id=\"toctogglecheckbox\" class=\"toctogglecheckbox\" style=\"display:none\" /><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en-GB\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2 id=\"mw-toc-heading\">Contents</h2><span class=\"toctogglespan\"><label class=\"toctogglelabel\" for=\"toctogglecheckbox\"></label></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Details\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Details</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Walkthrough\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Walkthrough</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Getting_started\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Getting started</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Finding_Father_Urhney\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Finding Father Urhney</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Freeing_the_ghosts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Freeing the ghosts</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Reward\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Reward</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#Required_for_completing\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Required for completing</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#Transcript\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Transcript</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-9\"><a href=\"#Trivia\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Trivia</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Details\">Details</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/The_Restless_Ghost?section=1&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Details\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/The_Restless_Ghost?action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Details\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<table class=\"questdetails plainlinks\" cellspacing=\"3\"><tbody><tr><th class=\"questdetails-header\">Start point</th><td class=\"questdetails-info\"><img alt=\"Quest point icon.png\" src=\"/images/thumb/Quest_point_icon.png/17px-Quest_point_icon.png?dc356\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"17\" height=\"17\" srcset=\"/images/Quest_point_icon.png?dc356 1.5x\" data-file-width=\"21\" data-file-height=\"21\" /> Speak to <a href=\"/w/Father_Aereck\" title=\"Father Aereck\">Father Aereck</a> in the chapel south-east of <a href=\"/w/Lumbridge_Castle\" title=\"Lumbridge Castle\">Lumbridge Castle</a>.</td></tr><tr><th class=\"questdetails-header\">Official difficulty</th><td class=\"questdetails-info\">Novice</td></tr><tr><th class=\"questdetails-header\">Description</th><td class=\"questdetails-info\">A ghost is haunting <a href=\"/w/Lumbridge\" title=\"Lumbridge\">Lumbridge</a> graveyard. The priest of the Lumbridge church of <a href=\"/w/Saradomin\" title=\"Saradomin\">Saradomin</a> wants you to find out how to get rid of it.</td></tr><tr><th class=\"questdetails-header\">Official length</th><td class=\"questdetails-info\">Short</td></tr><tr><th class=\"questdetails-header\">Requirements</th><td class=\"questdetails-info qc-input qc-active\">\nCapable of killing or running away from a <a href=\"/w/Combat_level\" title=\"Combat level\">combat level</a> 13 <a href=\"/w/Skeleton\" title=\"Skeleton\">skeleton</a>.</td></tr><tr><th class=\"questdetails-header\">Items required</th><td class=\"questdetails-info\">\nNone</td></tr><tr><th class=\"questdetails-header\">Recommended</th><td class=\"questdetails-info qc-active\">\n<div class=\"lighttable checklist no-toggle-parent\">\n<ul><li><span class=\"scp\" data-skill=\"Combat level\" data-level=\"10\"><a href=\"/w/Combat_level\" title=\"Combat level\"><img alt=\"Combat level\" src=\"/images/Attack_style_icon.png?ceb2e\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"21\" height=\"21\" data-file-width=\"19\" data-file-height=\"19\" /></a> 10 <a href=\"/w/Combat_level\" title=\"Combat level\">Combat level</a></span></li>\n<li>Three <a href=\"/w/Lumbridge_teleport\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Lumbridge teleport\">Lumbridge teleports</a></li>\n<li><i>(<a href=\"/w/Members\" title=\"Members\">Members</a> only)</i> <a href=\"/w/Necklace_of_Passage\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Necklace of Passage\">Necklace of Passage</a> to the Wizards' Tower</li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th class=\"questdetails-header\">Enemies to defeat</th><td class=\"questdetails-info\">\n<a href=\"/w/Skeleton_(The_Restless_Ghost)\" title=\"Skeleton (The Restless Ghost)\">Skeleton</a> <i>(level 13)</i> <i>(can be avoided)</i></td></tr></tbody></table><div class=\"hidden\" style=\"display:none\">&#123;&#34;requirements&#34;:&#34;Capable of killing or running away from a &#91;&#91;combat level&#93;&#93; 13 &#91;&#91;skeleton&#93;&#93;.&#34;,&#34;desc&#34;:&#34;A ghost is haunting &#91;&#91;Lumbridge&#93;&#93; graveyard. The priest of the Lumbridge church of &#91;&#91;Saradomin&#93;&#93; wants you to find out how to get rid of it.&#34;,&#34;difficulty&#34;:&#34;Novice&#34;,&#34;kills&#34;:&#34;&#91;&#91;Skeleton (The Restless Ghost)|Skeleton&#93;&#93; &#39;&#39;(level 13)&#39;&#39; &#39;&#39;(can be avoided)&#39;&#39;&#34;,&#34;name&#34;:&#34;The Restless Ghost&#34;,&#34;start&#34;:&#34;Speak to &#91;&#91;Father Aereck&#93;&#93; in the chapel south-east of &#91;&#91;Lumbridge Castle&#93;&#93;.&#34;,&#34;length&#34;:&#34;Short&#34;,&#34;items&#34;:&#34;None&#34;&#125;</div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Walkthrough\">Walkthrough</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/The_Restless_Ghost?section=2&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Walkthrough\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/The_Restless_Ghost?action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Walkthrough\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Getting_started\">Getting started</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/The_Restless_Ghost?section=3&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Getting started\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/The_Restless_Ghost?action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Getting started\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Talk to <a href=\"/w/Father_Aereck\" title=\"Father Aereck\">Father Aereck</a> located in the Lumbridge chapel just east of <a href=\"/w/Bob%27s_Brilliant_Axes\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Bob&#39;s Brilliant Axes\">Bob's Brilliant Axes</a>, and he will tell you that a <a href=\"/w/Restless_ghost\" title=\"Restless ghost\">ghost</a> is haunting the graveyard in <a href=\"/w/Lumbridge\" title=\"Lumbridge\">Lumbridge</a>. He needs you to help him. He wants you to talk to <a href=\"/w/Father_Urhney\" title=\"Father Urhney\">Father Urhney</a>, located in a house west of <a href=\"/w/Lumbridge_Swamp\" title=\"Lumbridge Swamp\">Lumbridge Swamp</a>, and get some information from him on ghosts.\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Finding_Father_Urhney\">Finding Father Urhney</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/The_Restless_Ghost?section=4&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Finding Father Urhney\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/The_Restless_Ghost?action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: Finding Father Urhney\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\"mw-kartographer-container thumb tleft\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width: 250px;\"><a class=\"mw-kartographer-map\" style=\"width: 250px; height: 250px;background-image: url(https://maps.runescape.wiki/osrs/versions/2022-03-23_a/tiles/rendered/0/2/0_48_50.png), url(https://maps.runescape.wiki/osrs/versions/2022-03-23_a/tiles/rendered/0/2/0_49_50.png), url(https://maps.runescape.wiki/osrs/versions/2022-03-23_a/tiles/rendered/0/2/0_48_49.png), url(https://maps.runescape.wiki/osrs/versions/2022-03-23_a/tiles/rendered/0/2/0_49_49.png); background-position: -179px -231px, 77px -231px, -179px 25px, 77px 25px; background-repeat: no-repeat;\" data-mw=\"interface\" data-style=\"0\" data-width=\"250\" data-height=\"250\" data-zoom=\"2\" data-lat=\"3175\" data-lon=\"3148\" data-mapid=\"0\" data-plane=\"0\" data-overlays=\"[&quot;_53a77fa857c1b6a135eec454d8696ab0e88f51f4&quot;]\" href=\"/w/Special:Map/0/2/-1/3148/3175\"></a><div class=\"thumbcaption\">Father Urhney's small house</div></div></div>\n<p>Go south of the castle, and then keep going west in the swamps. You'll soon come upon a small house. Go inside, and talk to <a href=\"/w/Father_Urhney\" title=\"Father Urhney\">Father Urhney</a> about <a href=\"/w/Father_Aereck\" title=\"Father Aereck\">Father Aereck</a> needing help with the <a href=\"/w/Restless_ghost\" title=\"Restless ghost\">ghost</a> haunting the graveyard. He will give you an <a href=\"/w/Amulet_of_ghostspeak\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Amulet of ghostspeak\">amulet of ghostspeak</a> so that you're able to talk to the ghost. It is advised to keep the amulet for future quests. Teleport back to Lumbridge (optional). Now, go back to the graveyard in <a href=\"/w/Lumbridge\" title=\"Lumbridge\">Lumbridge</a>, and go to the marble coffin that is located in a small house by the graveyard.\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Freeing_the_ghosts\">Freeing the ghosts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/The_Restless_Ghost?section=5&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Freeing the ghosts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/The_Restless_Ghost?action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: Freeing the ghosts\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Wear your <a href=\"/w/Amulet_of_ghostspeak\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Amulet of ghostspeak\">amulet of ghostspeak</a> and search the coffin. Talk to the <a href=\"/w/Restless_ghost\" title=\"Restless ghost\">ghost</a> who comes out. He will tell you he is missing his skull and wants you to get it for him. He will say he was near the <a href=\"/w/Wizards%27_Tower\" title=\"Wizards&#39; Tower\">Wizards' Tower</a> on an island south of <a href=\"/w/Draynor_Village\" title=\"Draynor Village\">Draynor Village</a>.\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/w/File:The_Restless_Ghost_-_Battle.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/The_Restless_Ghost_-_Battle.png/300px-The_Restless_Ghost_-_Battle.png?c1262\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"300\" height=\"201\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/The_Restless_Ghost_-_Battle.png/450px-The_Restless_Ghost_-_Battle.png?c1262 1.5x, /images/thumb/The_Restless_Ghost_-_Battle.png/600px-The_Restless_Ghost_-_Battle.png?c1262 2x\" data-file-width=\"723\" data-file-height=\"484\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/w/File:The_Restless_Ghost_-_Battle.png\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Fighting the Skeleton in the <a href=\"/w/Wizards%27_Tower\" title=\"Wizards&#39; Tower\">Wizards' Tower</a>.</div></div></div>\n<p>Head to the Wizards' Tower, and climb down the ladder in the room directly next to the entrance. Down the ladder you will find an altar. Search the altar. The <a href=\"/w/Ghost%27s_skull\" title=\"Ghost&#39;s skull\">ghost's skull</a> will be there, but when you grab it, a <a href=\"/w/Skeleton_(The_Restless_Ghost)\" title=\"Skeleton (The Restless Ghost)\">skeleton</a> will appear and attack you. <b>Fighting it is optional,</b> so kill it or run, and make sure you have the skull in your inventory. Teleport back to Lumbridge (optional). Then, go back to the Lumbridge graveyard.\n</p><p>Talk to the ghost. He'll want you to put it in his coffin. Use the skull with the coffin and he will rest in peace. You will see his spirit disappear into the river. When you have done this, you will have finished the quest.\n</p><p><b>Quest complete!</b>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Reward\">Reward</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/The_Restless_Ghost?section=6&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Reward\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/The_Restless_Ghost?action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: Reward\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"center\"><div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"/w/File:The_Restless_Ghost_reward_scroll.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"The Restless Ghost reward scroll.png\" src=\"/images/The_Restless_Ghost_reward_scroll.png?5828a\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"488\" height=\"320\" data-file-width=\"488\" data-file-height=\"320\" /></a></div></div>\n<ul><li>1 <a href=\"/w/Quest_points\" title=\"Quest points\"><img alt=\"Quest points\" src=\"/images/Quest_point_icon.png?dc356\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"21\" height=\"21\" data-file-width=\"21\" data-file-height=\"21\" /></a>  <a href=\"/w/Quest_points\" title=\"Quest points\">Quest point</a></li>\n<li><span class=\"scp\" data-skill=\"Prayer\" data-level=\"1,125\"><a href=\"/w/Prayer\" title=\"Prayer\"><img alt=\"Prayer\" src=\"/images/thumb/Prayer_icon.png/21px-Prayer_icon.png?ca0dc\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"21\" height=\"21\" srcset=\"/images/Prayer_icon.png?ca0dc 1.5x\" data-file-width=\"23\" data-file-height=\"23\" /></a> 1,125 </span> <a href=\"/w/Prayer\" title=\"Prayer\">Prayer</a> <a href=\"/w/Experience\" title=\"Experience\">experience</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Ghostspeak_amulet\" title=\"Ghostspeak amulet\">Ghostspeak amulet</a> (keep for <a href=\"/w/Creature_of_Fenkenstrain\" title=\"Creature of Fenkenstrain\">Creature of Fenkenstrain</a>)</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Required_for_completing\">Required for completing</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/The_Restless_Ghost?section=7&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Required for completing\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/The_Restless_Ghost?action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: Required for completing\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Completion of The Restless Ghost is required for the following:\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/w/Animal_Magnetism\" title=\"Animal Magnetism\">Animal Magnetism</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Cabin_Fever\" title=\"Cabin Fever\">Cabin Fever</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Curse_of_the_Empty_Lord\" title=\"Curse of the Empty Lord\">Curse of the Empty Lord</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Ghosts_Ahoy\" title=\"Ghosts Ahoy\">Ghosts Ahoy</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Making_History\" title=\"Making History\">Making History</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Nature_Spirit\" title=\"Nature Spirit\">Nature Spirit</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Creature_of_Fenkenstrain\" title=\"Creature of Fenkenstrain\">Creature of Fenkenstrain</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Transcript\">Transcript</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/The_Restless_Ghost?section=8&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Transcript\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/The_Restless_Ghost?action=edit&amp;section=8\" title=\"Edit section: Transcript\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<table class=\"messagebox hasdialogue plainlinks\" style=\"border: 0;\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<td align=\"center\">This article on a <a href=\"/w/Quest\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Quest\">quest</a> has an associated dialogue page.<br /><b><a href=\"/w/Transcript:The_Restless_Ghost\" title=\"Transcript:The Restless Ghost\">Click here</a></b> for a transcript of possible conversations encountered throughout the quest.\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Trivia\">Trivia</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/The_Restless_Ghost?section=9&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Trivia\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/The_Restless_Ghost?action=edit&amp;section=9\" title=\"Edit section: Trivia\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li>The Restless Ghost is one of 6 quests released on the launch day of <i><a href=\"/w/RuneScape\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"RuneScape\">RuneScape</a></i>.</li>\n<li>You can understand the ghost in the ending cutscene of the quest even without a ghostspeak amulet equipped.</li>\n<li>If the quest is completed with 0 Prayer experience, the reward increases the player's Prayer level from 1 to 9.</li></ul>\n<table class=\"navbox nowraplinks mw-collapsible\" data-expandtext=\"show\" data-navbox-name=\"The Restless Ghost\" data-collapsetext=\"hide\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" class=\"navbox-title\" id=\"navbox-title\"><div class=\"navbox-title-name-notplain\"><div class=\"navbar\" style=\"float:left;text-align:left;width:6em\"><div class=\"plainlinks noprint\" style=\"background-color:transparent;padding:0;font-weight:normal;font-size:xx-small;white-space:nowrap\"><a href=\"/w/Template:The_Restless_Ghost\" title=\"Template:The Restless Ghost\"><span title=\"View this template\">v</span></a>&#160;<span style=\"font-size:80%\">&#8226;</span>&#160;<a class=\"text\" href=\"https://oldschool.runescape.wiki/w/Template_talk:The_Restless_Ghost\"><span title=\"Discussion about this template\">d</span></a>&#160;<span style=\"font-size:80%\">&#8226;</span>&#160;<a class=\"text\" href=\"https://oldschool.runescape.wiki/w/Template:The_Restless_Ghost?action=edit\"><span title=\"Edit this template\">e</span></a></div></div><span><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">The Restless Ghost</a></span></div></th></tr><tr class=\"navbox-group\"><td class=\"navbox-group-title\">NPCs</td><td class=\"navbox-list navbox-parent\" style=\"padding:0\"><table class=\"navbox-subgroup nowraplinks\" data-expandtext=\"show\" data-collapsetext=\"hide\"><tbody><tr class=\"navbox-group navbox-group-split\"><td class=\"navbox-group-title-hidden\" colspan=\"0\" style=\"display:none\"></td><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"navbox-list\">\n<ul><li><span class=\"plink-template\"><a href=\"/w/Father_Aereck\" title=\"Father Aereck\"><img alt=\"Father Aereck chathead.png: Chat head image of Father Aereck\" src=\"/images/thumb/Father_Aereck_chathead.png/31px-Father_Aereck_chathead.png?82260\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"31\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/Father_Aereck_chathead.png/46px-Father_Aereck_chathead.png?82260 1.5x, /images/thumb/Father_Aereck_chathead.png/61px-Father_Aereck_chathead.png?82260 2x\" data-file-width=\"71\" data-file-height=\"81\" /></a></span><a href=\"/w/Father_Aereck\" title=\"Father Aereck\">Father Aereck</a></li>\n<li><span class=\"plink-template\"><a href=\"/w/Father_Urhney\" title=\"Father Urhney\"><img alt=\"Father Urhney chathead.png: Chat head image of Father Urhney\" src=\"/images/thumb/Father_Urhney_chathead.png/35px-Father_Urhney_chathead.png?cf65e\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"35\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/Father_Urhney_chathead.png/53px-Father_Urhney_chathead.png?cf65e 1.5x, /images/thumb/Father_Urhney_chathead.png/70px-Father_Urhney_chathead.png?cf65e 2x\" data-file-width=\"100\" data-file-height=\"100\" /></a></span><a href=\"/w/Father_Urhney\" title=\"Father Urhney\">Father Urhney</a></li>\n<li><span class=\"plink-template\"><a href=\"/w/Restless_ghost\" title=\"Restless ghost\"><img alt=\"Restless ghost chathead.png: Chat head image of Restless ghost\" src=\"/images/thumb/Restless_ghost_chathead.png/44px-Restless_ghost_chathead.png?1a2e5\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"44\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/Restless_ghost_chathead.png/66px-Restless_ghost_chathead.png?1a2e5 1.5x, /images/thumb/Restless_ghost_chathead.png/88px-Restless_ghost_chathead.png?1a2e5 2x\" data-file-width=\"149\" data-file-height=\"119\" /></a></span><a href=\"/w/Restless_ghost\" title=\"Restless ghost\">Restless ghost</a></li></ul></td></tr><tr class=\"navbox-group\"><td class=\"navbox-group-title\">Enemies</td><td class=\"navbox-list\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/w/Skeleton_(The_Restless_Ghost)\" title=\"Skeleton (The Restless Ghost)\">Skeleton</a></li></ul></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr><tr class=\"navbox-group\"><td class=\"navbox-group-title\">Items</td><td class=\"navbox-list\">\n<ul><li><span class=\"plink-template\"><a href=\"/w/Ghostspeak_amulet\" title=\"Ghostspeak amulet\"><img alt=\"Ghostspeak amulet.png\" src=\"/images/Ghostspeak_amulet.png?d2266\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"25\" height=\"28\" data-file-width=\"25\" data-file-height=\"28\" /></a></span><a href=\"/w/Ghostspeak_amulet\" title=\"Ghostspeak amulet\">Ghostspeak amulet</a></li>\n<li><span class=\"plink-template\"><a href=\"/w/Ghost%27s_skull\" title=\"Ghost&#39;s skull\"><img alt=\"Ghost&#39;s skull.png\" src=\"/images/Ghost%27s_skull.png?d2266\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"23\" height=\"31\" data-file-width=\"23\" data-file-height=\"31\" /></a></span><a href=\"/w/Ghost%27s_skull\" title=\"Ghost&#39;s skull\">Ghost's skull</a></li></ul></td></tr><tr class=\"navbox-group\"><td class=\"navbox-group-title\">Locations</td><td class=\"navbox-list\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/w/Lumbridge\" title=\"Lumbridge\">Lumbridge</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Lumbridge_Swamp\" title=\"Lumbridge Swamp\">Lumbridge Swamp</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Wizards%27_Tower\" title=\"Wizards&#39; Tower\">Wizards' Tower</a></li></ul></td></tr><tr class=\"navbox-group\"><td class=\"navbox-group-title\">Related</td><td class=\"navbox-list\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/w/The_Restless_Ghost/Quick_guide\" title=\"The Restless Ghost/Quick guide\">Quick Guide</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Transcript:The_Restless_Ghost\" title=\"Transcript:The Restless Ghost\">Transcript</a></li></ul></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nParsed by mediawiki‐67df7655d‐7qtxl\nCached time: 20220420171250\nCache expiry: 86400\nReduced expiry: false\nComplications: []\n[SMW] In‐text annotation parser time: 0.002 seconds\nCPU time usage: 0.116 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.144 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 532/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 22666/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 1669/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 9/100\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 985/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.028/10.000 seconds\nLua memory usage: 1340379/367001600 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   90.271      1 -total\n 21.65%   19.541      1 Template:Quest_details\n 19.49%   17.594      1 Template:The_Restless_Ghost\n 17.55%   15.846      2 Template:Navbox\n 14.63%   13.210      1 Template:Hastranscript\n 13.98%   12.623      1 Template:Map\n 13.38%   12.082      1 Template:External\n 13.01%   11.744      1 Template:Hastranscript/t\n  7.15%    6.458      1 Template:Infobox_Quest\n  5.50%    4.962      3 Template:SCP\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key en_osrswiki:pcache:idhash:2120-0!dateformat=default and timestamp 20220420171250 and revision id 14265909. Serialized with PHP.\n -->\n</div>","rawContent":"{{External|rs|rsc}}\n{{Redirect3|The Restless Ghost|For the non-player character featured in the quest, see [[Restless ghost]]}}\n{{Has quick guide}}\n{{Infobox Quest\n|name = The Restless Ghost\n|number = 3\n|image = [[File:The Restless Ghost.png|300px]]\n|release = [[4 January]] [[2001]]\n|update = Runescape beta is now online!\n|members = No\n|series = None\n|difficulty = Novice\n|developer = {{RSL|Paul Gower}}\n}}\nA ghost is haunting [[Lumbridge]] graveyard. The priest of the Lumbridge church of [[Saradomin]] wants you to find out how to get rid of it.\n\n==Details==\n{{Quest details\n|start = Speak to [[Father Aereck]] in the chapel south-east of [[Lumbridge Castle]].\n|difficulty = 1\n|description = A ghost is haunting [[Lumbridge]] graveyard. The priest of the Lumbridge church of [[Saradomin]] wants you to find out how to get rid of it.\n|length = Short\n|requirements = Capable of killing or running away from a [[combat level]] 13 [[skeleton]].\n|recommended = \n* {{SCP|Combat|10|link=yes}}\n*Three [[Lumbridge teleport]]s\n*''([[Members]] only)'' [[Necklace of Passage]] to the Wizards' Tower\n|kills = [[Skeleton (The Restless Ghost)|Skeleton]] ''(level 13)'' ''(can be avoided)''\n}}\n\n==Walkthrough==\n===Getting started===\nTalk to [[Father Aereck]] located in the Lumbridge chapel just east of [[Bob's Brilliant Axes]], and he will tell you that a [[Restless ghost|ghost]] is haunting the graveyard in [[Lumbridge]]. He needs you to help him. He wants you to talk to [[Father Urhney]], located in a house west of [[Lumbridge Swamp]], and get some information from him on ghosts.\n\n===Finding Father Urhney===\n{{Map|3144,3178|3152,3178|3152,3173|3144,3173|mtype=polygon|caption=Father Urhney's small house|align=left|width=250|height=250}}\nGo south of the castle, and then keep going west in the swamps. You'll soon come upon a small house. Go inside, and talk to [[Father Urhney]] about [[Father Aereck]] needing help with the [[Restless ghost|ghost]] haunting the graveyard. He will give you an [[amulet of ghostspeak]] so that you're able to talk to the ghost. It is advised to keep the amulet for future quests. Teleport back to Lumbridge (optional). Now, go back to the graveyard in [[Lumbridge]], and go to the marble coffin that is located in a small house by the graveyard.\n\n===Freeing the ghosts===\nWear your [[amulet of ghostspeak]] and search the coffin. Talk to the [[Restless ghost|ghost]] who comes out. He will tell you he is missing his skull and wants you to get it for him. He will say he was near the [[Wizards' Tower]] on an island south of [[Draynor Village]].\n[[File:The Restless Ghost - Battle.png|thumb|Fighting the Skeleton in the [[Wizards' Tower]].]]\nHead to the Wizards' Tower, and climb down the ladder in the room directly next to the entrance. Down the ladder you will find an altar. Search the altar. The [[ghost's skull]] will be there, but when you grab it, a [[Skeleton (The Restless Ghost)|skeleton]] will appear and attack you. '''Fighting it is optional,''' so kill it or run, and make sure you have the skull in your inventory. Teleport back to Lumbridge (optional). Then, go back to the Lumbridge graveyard.\n\nTalk to the ghost. He'll want you to put it in his coffin. Use the skull with the coffin and he will rest in peace. You will see his spirit disappear into the river. When you have done this, you will have finished the quest.\n\n'''Quest complete!'''\n\n==Reward==\n{{Quest rewards\n|name = The Restless Ghost\n|image = [[File:The Restless Ghost reward scroll.png|centre]]\n|qp = 1\n|rewards =\n*{{SCP|Prayer|1,125}} [[Prayer]] [[experience]]\n*[[Ghostspeak amulet]] (keep for [[Creature of Fenkenstrain]])\n}}\n\n==Required for completing==\nCompletion of The Restless Ghost is required for the following:\n* [[Animal Magnetism]]\n* [[Cabin Fever]]\n* [[Curse of the Empty Lord]]\n* [[Ghosts Ahoy]]\n* [[Making History]]\n* [[Nature Spirit]]\n* [[Creature of Fenkenstrain]]\n\n==Transcript==\n{{Hastranscript|quest}}\n\n==Trivia==\n* The Restless Ghost is one of 6 quests released on the launch day of ''[[RuneScape]]''.\n* You can understand the ghost in the ending cutscene of the quest even without a ghostspeak amulet equipped.\n* If the quest is completed with 0 Prayer experience, the reward increases the player's Prayer level from 1 to 9.\n\n{{The Restless Ghost}}"}